--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 10.1-0 (2012-03-01)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Updated ADMB from 10.0 to 10.1.

o Updated GCC from 4.5.0 to 4.5.2.

o Updated GDB from 7.2 to 7.4.

o Updated Emacs from 23.2.1 to 23.4.1.

o Updated admb-mode from 6.2 to 6.8.

o Disabled recentf-mode (for opening recent files), which had been causing long
  delays for many users.

o Added manual Texinfo file for archival purposes.

o Adopted new version numbering system, allowing for win32 and win64 builds.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 4.5.0-1 (2011-02-17)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Updated ADMB from 9.1 to 10.0.

o Updated GCC from 4.4.0 to 4.5.0.

o Updated GDB from 7.0.50 to 7.2.

o Updated Emacs from 23.1 to 23.2.1.

o Updated admb-mode from 4.0 to 6.2.

o Added menu entry and shortcut key C-p to open model file in other window.

o Added shortcut key C-- to toggle compilation flags.

o Added shortcut key S-return to end line and indent next line.

o Added shortcut key C-, to toggle whether trailing whitespace is highlighted
  and M-, to delete trailing whitespace.

o Added shortcut key S-f1 to show ADMB-IDE version.

o Added menu entry to show ADMB Mode version.

o Improved syntax highlighting of keywords.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 4.4.0-2 (2010-03-19)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Changed behavior of "View Report" to open report file inside ADMB-IDE.

o Changed "Run with Args" so it suggests the arguments that were last used.

o Added installation scripts for archival purposes.

o Added AUTODIF manual.

o Improved installer description and added configuration example to manual.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 4.4.0-1 (2010-03-14)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Updated ADMB from 9.0.363 to 9.1.

o Updated GCC from 3.4.5 to 4.4.0.

o Updated GDB from 6.8 to 7.0.50.

o Updated admb-mode from 3.5 to 4.0.

o Added menu entries "View Point Estimates" and "View Initial Values".

o Improved syntax highlighting of keywords, libraries, namespaces, and function
  names.

o Input and output files (ctl/dat/pin and par/rep) are opened in conf-unix-mode
  to provide syntax highlighting of #comments.

o Improved code template.

o Improved C-S-home and C-S-end selection.

o Added chapter about Emacs configuration to manual.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 3.4.5-8 (2009-09-14)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Updated admb-mode from 3.4 to 3.5.

o Added menu entry and shortcut key C-. to toggle whether a section indicator is
  shown in the mode line.

o Added shortcut key C-space to expand recognized words, found elsewhere in the
  code.

o Added shortcut key S-f9 to run model executable with arguments.

o Improved syntax highlighting of function names.

o Added paragraph about indentation to manual.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 3.4.5-7 (2009-09-06)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Updated ADMB from 9.0.202 to 9.0.363.

o Updated Emacs from 22.3 to 23.1.

o Updated ADMB-RE manual.

o Added viper-mode information to manual.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 3.4.5-6 (2009-07-07)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Updated admb-mode from 3.3 to 3.4.

o Improved commands "Run" and "Run with Args" so ADMB-IDE doesn't hang up while
  model runs and optimization progress is reported live.

o Added shortcut key M-f6 to switch to next buffer in Linux KDE.

o Added ADMB and ADMB-RE manuals.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 3.4.5-5 (2009-06-03)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Updated admb-mode from 3.1 to 3.3.

o Improved filename handling and added current directory to local Linux path.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 3.4.5-4 (2009-05-29)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Minor improvements in manual and shortcut icon.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 3.4.5-3 (2009-05-28)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Minor improvements in manual and installer.




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADMB-IDE 3.4.5-2 (2009-05-27)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Updated admb-mode from 3.0 to 3.1.

o Bound M-a, M-b, M-e, M-f, M-h, M-o, and M-t to activate the menu bar. Bound
  Alt to activate the menu bar (Windows only). Unbound S-f11.

o Added manual sections describing menu bar activation, undo/redo, and how to
  use ADMB-IDE without overwriting the current .emacs file. Improved directions
  for setting up ADMB-IDE.




